.png\" />"},{"pid":"7c05e4662cb5018af0988815898436ff6429c6c7","tid":1935454,"uid":229834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:47:34.000Z","msg":"5 ho 推。。。"},{"pid":"47e5c3c9735855764042c93bff45fad27c131cf3","tid":1935454,"uid":229834,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:47:56.000Z","msg":"講真 ng ho再推...."},{"pid":"e67ac7a6ce46ca188aede8d07b8de7d23004cb77","tid":1935454,"uid":229834,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:48:36.000Z","msg":"講真，樓主你如果發出黎，我真係會報警，等警察上你屋企打個轉黎判斷你有冇犯法，我係認真，唔係講緊笑，你話我報警lun，正義lun，乜都好，隨便你。<br />\n<br />\n你有無想過你呢種一時之快會對當事人有幾大傷害？傳左出去人地點見人，張相仲要咁清？你地班友可能就睇得好happy，人地分分鐘就躲係屋企喊。人有時好脆弱，個傻閪有乜事的話，你良心過唔過意得去？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我勸你放出黎之前三思一下，唔好受班花生友影響，呢度D人有野睇就唔會理他人感受，當中仲有成班小朋友字都未識得幾個，希望你可以作出獨立判斷，唔好助長網絡暴力，做埋晒D損人不利己的事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 你果度我冇睇錯係黃大仙黎，要搵你住邊計下角度就知，IP 都唔洗check"},{"pid":"8b7060088b8aa666433417106472aea5e2968845","tid":1935454,"uid":227275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cool-style.pixfs.net/cool/2020/02/49559949267_3da049d7ab_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcool-style.pixfs.net%2Fcool%2F2020%2F02%2F49559949267_3da049d7ab_b.jpg&h=3dd282d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成個派大星咁撚樣"},{"pid":"460fcdcbdf228ca5e1f8fac75d335eeb545b4ef8","tid":1935454,"uid":351498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:49:14.000Z","msg":"又係啲自私柒頭"},{"pid":"6636767c0843ce94392fb5289b8e219aa71c9c44","tid":1935454,"uid":229834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:49:20.000Z","msg":"真係唔好推"},{"pid":"d808be1752bfcd8fe103eaeca2020373e35a4927","tid":1935454,"uid":229834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:49:45.000Z","msg":"咪推"},{"pid":"1c53c8b716def36e249326d9c77695be012077a2","tid":1935454,"uid":229834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T